## ✨ **KEY FEATURES**

- **🧠 Hybrid AI Architecture**: Combines symbolic reasoning with neural networks
- **📊 Multi-Model Fusion**: Transparent weighted combination (30%+50%+20%)
- **🔍 Explainable AI**: SHAP values + rule traces + feature importance
- **🌐 Web Interface**: User-friendly Gradio dashboard with 3 modes
- **📱 Dual Deployment**: Local CPU/GPU or Google Colab with TPU
- **📚 Evidence-Based**: WHO/CDC guidelines integrated
- **🎯 High Accuracy**: 99% (clinical) + CNN trained on 24K images
- **📦 One-Click Setup**: Automated dataset download + preprocessing

